# Playwright Downloads

Downloads are emitted as events. Start waiting before the click or navigation that triggers the file.

```typescript
const downloadPromise = page.waitForEvent('download');
await page.getByRole('button', { name: 'Export CSV' }).click();
const download = await downloadPromise;
await download.saveAs(`artifacts/${download.suggestedFilename()}`);
```

The downloaded temporary file is tied to the browser context. Call `saveAs()` before closing the context or browser.
